NOTES
------
CLI
    ./configure
    make
    make install
PHP Ext
    install php with debug options
    ini_params

KEY TROUBLES
    general
        reverse order & mixed chars
        eg:
            ORIG      -> ABCDEF
            FOR CLASS -> FEDCBA -> FDBECA
    EXT
        key_file from php.ini (global)
            else
        key_file from path (for each project)

        file bonzai.ini in the same path of module (.so or .dll)
            bonzai_ini (opt) - to get option
    CLASS
        set path via php (insecure!)

First release
    no obfuscator
    i18n -> IT, EN
    docs -> IT, EN

php class
    clean/dirty version (with the tool to obfuscate)
    mod phpinfo()...if possible
